title: Thank you to Reviewers and Editors 2023
content: Editor-in-Chief Yunde Zhao and the staff of Plant Physiology thank the reviewers listed below, whose insight and contributions in reviewing manuscripts from January 1 to December 31, 2023, have helped make the journal a success. We would also like to thank the Associate Editors, Monitoring Editors, and Assistant Features Editors for their contributions to the journal and recognize those Editors who have concluded their term of service, as well as those who joined the Editorial Board in 2023.
